<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="Barbell-Shrug">Barbell Shrug</h3>



<p><a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/barbell-shrug" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Barbell Shrugs</a> benefit your trapezius muscles and strengthen your upper back. You can use this barbell workout to strengthen your shoulder or for full-body workouts.</p>



<p>Barbell Shrugs are suitable for people who want to experience upper-back development and attain strong shoulders. You can still focus on this <a href="https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/medicine-and-dentistry/triceps-brachii-muscle" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">barbell triceps workout</a> if you are an athlete.&nbsp;</p>



<p>However, this overhead shoulder press exercise is unsuitable if you have shoulder joint injuries. It is a good idea to embrace this <a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/chest-and-arm-workout" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">chest and arms workout</a> by performing small <a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6835758/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">muscle activations</a> to achieve the best results. If you are a beginner, start with small weights as you graduate to handle heavier ones.</p>



